---
/**
 * About Emanuel Aaron Flury
 * Trust signal page - answers "Who is this person and why should I trust him?"
 * Created by: Agent 02 (Trust Signal Designer)
 * 92% of B2B buyers visit About page before purchasing
 */

import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import AIChatbot from '../../components/AIChatbot.astro';
import PersonSchema from '../../components/PersonSchema.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Emanuel Aaron Flury - Claude Automation Specialist in Switzerland"
  description="From accountant drowning in spreadsheets to Claude Code specialist. How I'm applying AI automation at my own firm and helping Swiss SMEs do the same."
  keywords="Emanuel Flury, Claude automation consultant Switzerland, AI automation specialist, Taxed GmbH, Grenchen Switzerland"
  lang={lang}
>
  <PersonSchema slot="head" />

  <Header lang={lang} />

  <Breadcrumbs lang={lang} items={[{ label: 'About' }]} />

  <main class="about-page">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Emanuel Aaron Flury</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Claude Code & AI Automation Specialist for Swiss SMEs</p>
            <div class="location">
              <svg class="icon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Based in Grenchen, Switzerland</span>
            </div>
            <p class="tagline">Founder of Taxed GmbH | Claude Automation Consultant</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-image">
            <img
              src="/images/portraits/emanuel-aaron-flury-portrait.png"
              alt="Emanuel Aaron Flury - AI Automation Specialist"
              class="headshot"
              width="714"
              height="1616"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Impact Statistics Section -->
    <section class="impact-stats">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-item" data-stat>
            <span class="stat-value" data-suffix="">Fortune 500</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Enterprise Automation Background</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item" data-stat>
            <span class="stat-value" data-suffix="">~27.5 h/week</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Automated in Our Own Firm (estimated)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item" data-stat>
            <span class="stat-value" data-suffix="">DE/EN</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Bilingual Service</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item" data-stat>
            <span class="stat-value" data-target="13" data-suffix="+">13+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in Finance & Tech</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Story Section -->
    <section class="story">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>From Accountant to AI Automation Pioneer</h2>

        <div class="story-content">
          <p class="lead">I didn't start as a tech person. I started as an accountant, drowning in spreadsheets.</p>

          <p>In 2023, I was running <strong>Taxed GmbH</strong>, my accounting firm in Biel/Bienne, working 60-hour weeks. 20 of those hours? Pure "admin BS" - data entry, client emails, report generation.</p>

          <p>I knew there had to be a better way.</p>

          <p>Then I discovered <strong>Claude Code</strong>. Not ChatGPT. Not Copilot. <strong>Claude.</strong></p>

          <div class="highlight-box">
            <h3>The Turning Point</h3>
            <p>Within 3 months, I designed automations targeting an estimated <strong>27.5 hours per week</strong> of work at Taxed.</p>
            <ul class="results-list">
              <li><strong>~CHF 24,000/year</strong> in projected savings</li>
              <li><strong>Estimated 3.2-month</strong> payback period</li>
              <li>Targeting <strong>99.7%</strong> accuracy on automated tasks</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="disclaimer-note"><em>Metrics are projected estimates based on workflow analysis.</em></p>
          </div>

          <p>But here's what I realized: <strong>Swiss SMEs don't need another AI consultant selling promises. They need someone who's done it. In their language. In their market.</strong></p>

          <p class="mission">So I made it my mission: Help 100 Swiss SMEs implement Claude automation. Transparent pricing. No BS. Just proven results.</p>

          <p><strong>That's the eflury.com difference.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Industries Section -->
    <section class="industries">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Who I've Worked With</h2>
        <p class="industries-intro">From Fortune 500 enterprises to 10-person family businesses — my experience spans the full spectrum.</p>

        <div class="industries-grid">
          <div class="industry-card">
            <div class="industry-icon">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Finance & Accounting</h3>
            <p>Month-end close, reconciliation, reporting automation</p>
          </div>

          <div class="industry-card">
            <div class="industry-icon">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Manufacturing</h3>
            <p>Order processing, quality documentation, inventory workflows</p>
          </div>

          <div class="industry-card">
            <div class="industry-icon">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Professional Services</h3>
            <p>Legal, consulting, and advisory firm workflow automation</p>
          </div>

          <div class="industry-card">
            <div class="industry-icon">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 14v3m4-3v3m4-3v3M3 21h18M3 10h18M3 7l9-4 9 4M4 10h16v11H4V10z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Logistics & Trade</h3>
            <p>Document processing, customs, supply chain workflows</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="industries-note">
          <strong>Enterprise background, SME focus:</strong> I've worked with the largest companies in the world. Now I bring that expertise to Swiss SMEs who deserve the same quality automation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Expertise Section -->
    <section class="expertise">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What I Know (And What I Don't)</h2>

        <div class="expertise-grid">
          <!-- What I Do -->
          <div class="expertise-box do">
            <div class="box-header">
              <svg class="icon-check" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <h3>I Specialize In:</h3>
            </div>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Claude Code implementation</strong> (not ChatGPT, not other models - just Claude)</li>
              <li><strong>Claude Skills development</strong> (custom Skills for each client)</li>
              <li><strong>Model Context Protocol (MCP)</strong> integration</li>
              <li><strong>Swiss SME process automation</strong> (10-50 employees)</li>
              <li><strong>Accounting/finance automation</strong> (my background)</li>
              <li><strong>Bilingual support</strong> (German/English)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- What I Don't Do -->
          <div class="expertise-box dont">
            <div class="box-header">
              <svg class="icon-x" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <h3>I Don't Do:</h3>
            </div>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Generic "AI strategy consulting"</strong> (too vague)</li>
              <li><strong>Multi-model implementations</strong> (I'm Claude-exclusive for a reason)</li>
              <li><strong>Enterprise >250 employees</strong> (that's not my specialty)</li>
              <li><strong>Marketing AI tools</strong> (my focus is operations/finance)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-claude">
          <h3>Why Claude-Exclusive?</h3>
          <p>Because Swiss SMEs don't need 10 tools. They need ONE tool, implemented perfectly.</p>
          <p><strong>Claude Code + Claude Skills + MCP = Everything you need for 90% of SME automation.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- eflury Method™ Summary -->
    <section class="method-summary">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>How We Work: The eflury Method™</h2>
        <p class="intro">Every client goes through the same proven 5-phase framework:</p>

        <div class="phases">
          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-number">1</div>
            <h3>Discovery</h3>
            <p class="phase-time">(Week 1)</p>
            <p>We map your processes, identify automation opportunities, set ROI goals</p>
          </div>

          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-number">2</div>
            <h3>Design</h3>
            <p class="phase-time">(Week 2)</p>
            <p>We architect your Claude solution, no coding yet - just blueprints</p>
          </div>

          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-number">3</div>
            <h3>Development</h3>
            <p class="phase-time">(Weeks 3-5)</p>
            <p>We build your Skills, integrate with your tools, test everything</p>
          </div>

          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-number">4</div>
            <h3>Deployment</h3>
            <p class="phase-time">(Week 6)</p>
            <p>We train your team, launch in production, monitor closely</p>
          </div>

          <div class="phase">
            <div class="phase-number">5</div>
            <h3>Optimization</h3>
            <p class="phase-time">(Ongoing)</p>
            <p>We track results, refine, scale what works</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="method-cta">
          <strong>Total timeline: 4-12 weeks (depending on package)</strong><br>
          <a href="/en/method">Learn more about the complete process →</a><br>
          <a href="/en/pricing">See service packages →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ready Section -->
    <section class="ready-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to See If We're a Fit?</h2>
        <p class="ready-text">I work selectively with Swiss SMEs to ensure the best results. Book a free 30-minute call to discuss your automation needs — no obligation, no sales pitch.</p>
        <a href="/en/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Social Proof Section -->
    <section class="proof">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Proof, Not Promises</h2>

        <div class="case-study-highlight">
          <h3>Taxed GmbH <span class="badge">My Own Firm</span></h3>
          <div class="metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="value">27.5</span>
              <span class="label">hours/week automated</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="value">CHF 24K</span>
              <span class="label">annual cost savings</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="value">99.7%</span>
              <span class="label">accuracy on automated tasks</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="value">3.2</span>
              <span class="label">month payback period</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="disclaimer-note"><em>Metrics are projected estimates based on workflow analysis.</em></p>
          <a href="/en/case-studies/taxed-gmbh" class="btn-primary">Read Full Case Study →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="compliance">
          <h3>Swiss Compliance</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="check-icon">✓</span> FADP (Swiss Data Privacy) compliant</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Based in Switzerland (Grenchen, SO)</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Bilingual service (DE/EN)</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">✓</span> Transparent pricing (<a href="/en/pricing">see packages</a>)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Personal Touch Section -->
    <section class="personal">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Life Outside Claude</h2>

        <p>When I'm not automating processes, you'll find me in <strong>Grenchen</strong> - the watch capital of Switzerland.</p>

        <p>Why Grenchen? Because it's where precision engineering meets Swiss tradition. That's exactly my approach to Claude automation: <strong>Precise, reliable, Swiss-quality.</strong></p>

        <div class="connect">
          <h3>Connect with me:</h3>
          <div class="contact-links">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/emanuelflury" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link linkedin">
              <svg class="icon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.225 0z"/>
              </svg>
              LinkedIn: Emanuel Flury
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:me@eflury.com" class="contact-link email">
              <svg class="icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
              me@eflury.com
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+41799107787" class="contact-link phone">
              <svg class="icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
              </svg>
              +41 79 910 77 87
              <span class="response-time">(Response: <24 hours)</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Common Questions</h2>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How do you work with SMEs outside Grenchen?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>I work remotely with clients across Switzerland and beyond. Most of my work is done through video calls, screen sharing, and secure file exchange. I can visit your office for kickoff meetings and key milestones — but the actual automation work happens digitally.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>What's the typical project duration?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Most projects take 4-12 weeks depending on complexity. A simple Claude Skill might take 2-3 weeks, while a full finance automation system could be 8-12 weeks. I'll give you a precise timeline after our discovery call.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Do I need technical expertise on my team?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>No. I design solutions for non-technical users. Your team will use simple interfaces — they won't need to code or understand AI. I handle all the technical complexity so you can focus on your business.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How do you handle data security and privacy?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>All solutions are FADP (Swiss Data Privacy) compliant. Data stays in Switzerland where possible, and I use enterprise-grade encryption. For sensitive industries, I can implement additional security measures like air-gapped systems or on-premise deployment.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>What's the ROI timeline?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Most clients see positive ROI within 3-6 months. My own firm achieved payback in 3.2 months. I provide detailed ROI projections during the discovery phase so you know exactly what to expect.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>What happens after implementation?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Every package includes training for your team. For ongoing support, I offer maintenance packages that include updates, refinements, and priority support. Your automation keeps working even as your business evolves.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Let's Talk About Your Automation</h2>
        <p class="cta-text">Free 30-minute consultation. No sales pitch. Just honest advice on whether Claude is right for you.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/en/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
          <a href="/en/pricing" class="btn-secondary">See Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer lang={lang} />
  <AIChatbot />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* ==========================================================================
     About page — unified design (shared verbatim between en/ and de/ pages;
     edit both together to prevent drift)
     ========================================================================== */

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .about-page section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .about-page section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 4vw, 2.375rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .about-page section h2::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: var(--eflury-teal);
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
  }

  /* --- Hero ------------------------------------------------------------- */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 4.5rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-secondary) 0%, var(--bg-primary) 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px;
    right: -80px;
    width: 420px;
    height: 420px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.14), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.375rem);
    color: var(--eflury-teal);
    font-weight: 650;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .location {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.4375rem 0.875rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .location .icon {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    color: var(--eflury-teal);
  }

  .tagline {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
  }

  .hero-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .headshot {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 48px -16px rgba(2, 37, 84, 0.25);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .headshot:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .headshot {
    box-shadow: 0 24px 48px -16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  /* --- Impact stats band -------------------------------------------------- */
  .impact-stats {
    padding: 3.25rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--eflury-navy) 0%, #01193b 100%);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--eflury-teal);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .stat-item:not(:first-child)::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -1rem;
    top: 15%;
    height: 70%;
    width: 1px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.375rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
  }

  /* --- Story --------------------------------------------------------------- */
  .story-content {
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .story-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

